Once done simply call `mMediaProjection.stop()` to finish the recording and save the video as `tmp`
After which you can crop the video at the `xy` coordinates that your view is position using [FFmpeg][1]

    ffmpeg -i in.mp4 -filter:v &quot;crop=out_w:out_h:x:y&quot; out.mp4

